00052 #define MIN_FATAL(__format__,__args__ ...)\
00053 do{\
00054         Text *txt = tx_create(" ");\
00055         MinLogger *logger = mnl_get_logger_instance();\
00056         if (logger!=INITPTR) {\
00057                 tx_c_append(txt,"   ");\
00058                 tx_c_append(txt,mnl_get_component_name());\
00059                 tx_c_append(txt," ");\
00060                 tx_int_append(txt,"06",getpid());\
00061                 tx_c_append(txt," ");\
00062                 tx_c_append(txt,__FILE__);\
00063                 tx_c_append(txt,":");\
00064                 tx_int_append(txt,"04",__LINE__);\
00065                 tx_c_append(txt,":");\
00066                 tx_c_append(txt,__FUNCTION__);\
00067                 tx_c_append(txt,"() ");\
00068                 tx_c_append(txt,__format__);\
00069                 mnl_log(logger,ESFatal,tx_share_buf(txt),##__args__);\
00070         }\
00071         tx_destroy(&txt);\
00072 } while (0)
